Preheat oven to 375 degrees F. Heat a large ovenproof saute pan to medium heat. Add half of olive oil, then onions. Saute 2 minutes. Remove onions to a plate; add rest of olive oil and brown chicken on both sides. Return onions to pan and sprinkle all with Mrs. Dash(R) Fiesta Lime Blend. Toss again and add orange juice. Cook in oven 3-4 minutes. Remove. Rest 2 minutes and plate spooning onions and juice over chicken.